<item>
            <title>[LU-15910] ROOT default LMV is not working for subdirectory mount</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15910</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In subdirectory mount, the filesystem-wide default LMV doesn&apos;t take effect. There are two things need to be done:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;enforce the filesystem-wide default LMV on subdirectory mount if it&apos;s not set separately.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&quot;lfs getdirstripe -D &amp;lt;subdir_mount&amp;gt;&quot; should print the filesystem-wide default LMV.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
